1
00:00:01,502 --> 00:00:04,296
[ PANTING ]

2
00:00:27,653 --> 00:00:28,946
[ GRUNTS ]

3
00:00:28,946 --> 00:00:31,824
[ PANTING ]

4
00:00:35,619 --> 00:00:38,079
[ SNARLING ]

5
00:00:43,293 --> 00:00:45,921
[ SCREAMING ]

6
00:00:53,052 --> 00:00:58,433
♪ IT'S BEEN A LONG ROAD ♪

7
00:00:58,433 --> 00:01:01,269
♪ GETTING FROM THERE TO HERE ♪

8
00:01:01,269 --> 00:01:05,315
♪ IT'S BEEN A LONG TIME ♪

9
00:01:05,315 --> 00:01:08,944
♪ BUT MY TIME IS FINALLY NEAR ♪

10
00:01:08,944 --> 00:01:13,323
♪ AND I WILL SEE MY DREAM
COME ALIVE AT LAST ♪

11
00:01:13,323 --> 00:01:17,077
♪ I WILL TOUCH THE SKY ♪

12
00:01:17,077 --> 00:01:20,998
♪ AND THEY'RE NOT GONNA
HOLD ME DOWN NO MORE ♪

13
00:01:20,998 --> 00:01:24,376
♪ NO, THEY'RE NOT GONNA
CHANGE MY MIND ♪

14
00:01:24,376 --> 00:01:26,503
♪ 'CAUSE I'VE GOT FAITH ♪

15
00:01:26,503 --> 00:01:28,797
♪ OF THE HEART ♪

16
00:01:28,797 --> 00:01:31,884
♪ I'M GOING WHERE MY HEART
WILL TAKE ME ♪

17
00:01:31,884 --> 00:01:36,805
♪ I'VE GOT FAITH TO BELIEVE ♪

18
00:01:36,805 --> 00:01:39,850
♪ I CAN DO ANYTHING ♪

19
00:01:39,850 --> 00:01:43,604
♪ I'VE GOT STRENGTH
OF THE SOUL ♪

20
00:01:43,604 --> 00:01:47,441
♪ AND NO ONE'S GONNA BEND
OR BREAK ME ♪

21
00:01:47,441 --> 00:01:52,112
♪ I CAN REACH ANY STAR ♪

22
00:01:53,154 --> 00:01:54,698
♪ I'VE GOT FAITH ♪

23
00:01:54,698 --> 00:01:56,784
♪ I'VE GOT, I'VE GOT, I'VE GOT ♪

24
00:01:56,784 --> 00:02:00,788
♪ I'VE GOT FAITH ♪

25
00:02:00,788 --> 00:02:05,500
♪ FAITH OF THE HEART ♪

26
00:02:20,474 --> 00:02:21,934
[ DOORBELL CHIMES ]

27
00:02:21,934 --> 00:02:23,518
COME IN.

28
00:02:25,854 --> 00:02:28,732
THANKS FOR SEEING ME SO LATE.
YOU SURE I'M NOT BOTHERING YOU?

29
00:02:28,732 --> 00:02:30,191
NOT AT ALL.

30
00:02:30,191 --> 00:02:31,860
GEORGIA PEACHES.

31
00:02:31,860 --> 00:02:34,446
I PICKED UP A CRATE
WHEN WE WERE BACK ON EARTH.

32
00:02:34,446 --> 00:02:36,364
CHEF'S BEEN KEEPING THEM
IN STASIS FOR ME.

33
00:02:36,364 --> 00:02:38,617
THEY'RE AS FRESH
AS THE DAY THEY WERE PICKED.

34
00:02:38,617 --> 00:02:40,368
THANK YOU.

35
00:02:40,368 --> 00:02:41,536
AREN'T YOU GONNA TRY ONE?

36
00:02:41,536 --> 00:02:45,499
I DON'T USUALLY EAT THIS LATE.

37
00:02:45,499 --> 00:02:48,127
COME ON.
ONE BITE?

38
00:02:50,169 --> 00:02:51,505
HUH?

39
00:03:02,474 --> 00:03:05,936
THIS DOESN'T MAKE UP FOR
THE TWO SESSIONS YOU CANCELLED.

40
00:03:07,104 --> 00:03:08,856
MAYBE YOU HAVEN'T NOTICED,

41
00:03:08,856 --> 00:03:10,941
BUT I'VE BEEN
A LITTLE BUSY LATELY.

42
00:03:10,941 --> 00:03:13,152
IT'S NOT LIKE
I DIDN'T WANT TO COME BACK.

43
00:03:13,152 --> 00:03:16,321
AFTER OUR LAST SESSION,
I SLEPT LIKE A BABY.

44
00:03:16,321 --> 00:03:18,448
FIRST TIME IN MONTHS.

45
00:03:20,450 --> 00:03:23,078
[ SIGHS ]
SO SHOULD I JUST...

46
00:03:23,078 --> 00:03:24,371
PLEASE.

47
00:03:31,503 --> 00:03:34,422
-YOUR SHOES AS WELL.
-SHOES?

48
00:03:34,422 --> 00:03:37,217
THERE ARE MANY NEURAL NODES
IN THE SOLES OF THE FEET.

49
00:03:37,217 --> 00:03:39,553
HOLD ON. YOU NEVER
SAID ANYTHING ABOUT FEET.

50
00:03:39,553 --> 00:03:42,305
IS THAT A PROBLEM?

51
00:03:42,305 --> 00:03:44,641
WELL, FOR ONE THING, I HAVEN'T
HAD A SHOWER SINCE THIS MORNING,

52
00:03:44,641 --> 00:03:47,561
AND I KNOW HOW SENSITIVE THAT
VULCAN NOSE OF YOURS CAN BE.

53
00:03:47,561 --> 00:03:51,398
AND I'M A LITTLE TICKLISH.

54
00:03:52,524 --> 00:03:54,651
MAYBE MORE THAN A LITTLE.

55
00:03:54,651 --> 00:03:57,487
I'LL STOP AT THE FIRST SIGN
OF DISCOMFORT.

56
00:03:57,487 --> 00:03:58,989
YEAH.

57
00:04:04,078 --> 00:04:05,537
[ SIGHS ]

58
00:04:12,878 --> 00:04:15,797
OH!
YOUR HANDS ARE ICE-COLD.

59
00:04:22,596 --> 00:04:24,514
LONG, DEEP BREATHS.

60
00:04:24,514 --> 00:04:26,266
[ BREATHING DEEPLY ]

61
00:04:30,687 --> 00:04:32,480
YOU SURE THIS IS SAFE?

62
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:35,943
I MEAN, HAS ANYONE EVER TRIED IT
ON A HUMAN BEFORE?

63
00:04:35,943 --> 00:04:38,195
NOT TO MY KNOWLEDGE.

64
00:04:38,195 --> 00:04:41,364
THE RISK OF PARALYSIS
IS MINIMAL.

65
00:04:42,991 --> 00:04:44,284
BREATHE.

66
00:04:44,284 --> 00:04:46,245
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

67
00:04:49,330 --> 00:04:51,541
OH, THAT'S THE SPOT.

68
00:04:52,709 --> 00:04:54,628
[ BEEPS ]

69
00:04:58,966 --> 00:05:01,760
-T'POL.
-It's the captain.

70
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:05,222
I'd like you to join me in
the command center right away.

71
00:05:08,558 --> 00:05:10,269
[ DOOR OPENS ]

72
00:05:11,561 --> 00:05:14,606
-SORRY IF I WOKE YOU.
-I WASN'T ASLEEP.

73
00:05:14,606 --> 00:05:16,275
LOOK AT THIS.

74
00:05:22,572 --> 00:05:25,200
ANOTHER SPECIES OF XINDI?

75
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:27,410
ACCORDING TO PHLOX,
THEY PROBABLY EVOLVED

76
00:05:27,410 --> 00:05:30,413
FROM SOME FORM
OF ARBOREAL PRIMATE.

77
00:05:31,957 --> 00:05:35,085
I MANAGED TO PIECE TOGETHER
SOME OF THEIR STAR CHARTS.

78
00:05:37,462 --> 00:05:39,380
IT TOOK ME HALF THE NIGHT
TO FIGURE OUT

79
00:05:39,380 --> 00:05:42,176
HOW THEY MAP COORDINATES,
BUT I'VE BEEN ABLE
TO RECONSTRUCT

80
00:05:42,176 --> 00:05:44,636
THE SHIP'S COURSE
OVER THE PAST FEW MONTHS.

81
00:05:47,430 --> 00:05:49,224
THIS IS THE LAST PLANET
THEY VISITED

82
00:05:49,224 --> 00:05:50,892
BEFORE THEY WERE ATTACKED
BY THE MARAUDERS.

83
00:05:50,892 --> 00:05:52,894
DOES IT SAY
WHAT THEY WERE DOING THERE?

84
00:05:52,894 --> 00:05:56,439
NO.
BUT IT'S ONLY A DAY AWAY.

85
00:05:57,899 --> 00:06:00,652
WE DON'T KNOW IF THESE XINDI
WERE INVOLVED

86
00:06:00,652 --> 00:06:02,403
WITH THE ONES
WHO ATTACKED EARTH.

87
00:06:03,530 --> 00:06:05,532
WE DON'T KNOW THEY WEREN'T.

88
00:06:05,532 --> 00:06:08,118
TELL TRAVIS TO SET A COURSE.

89
00:06:11,663 --> 00:06:13,498
[ DOOR OPENS ]

90
00:06:20,463 --> 00:06:22,507
THE ECOSYSTEM IS PROLIFIC.

91
00:06:22,507 --> 00:06:24,176
THERE ARE SEVERAL MILLION

92
00:06:24,176 --> 00:06:25,510
CHROMOPHYLLIC PLANT SPECIES
ALONE.

93
00:06:25,510 --> 00:06:26,887
WHAT ABOUT XINDI?

94
00:06:26,887 --> 00:06:29,430
I'M NOT DETECTING
ANY HUMANOID LIFE.

95
00:06:29,430 --> 00:06:33,143
BUT IT'LL TAKE SEVERAL
HOURS TO SEARCH ALL
OF THE LAND MASSES.

96
00:06:33,143 --> 00:06:35,020
[ BEEPING ]

97
00:06:35,020 --> 00:06:38,481
CAPTAIN, I'M PICKING UP
A METALLIC SIGNATURE

98
00:06:38,481 --> 00:06:41,484
AT THE NORTHERN END
OF THOSE EQUATORIAL ISLANDS.

99
00:06:41,484 --> 00:06:43,611
IT LOOKS LIKE A LANDING CRAFT.

100
00:06:43,611 --> 00:06:45,488
ANY BIO-SCANS?

101
00:06:45,488 --> 00:06:48,658
NONE WITHIN
A 30-KILOMETER RADIUS.

102
00:07:01,796 --> 00:07:04,216
ANOTHER 13 KILOMETERS.

103
00:07:06,134 --> 00:07:09,137
THERE'S A BREAK IN THE CANOPY.
IT SHOULD BE WIDE ENOUGH.

104
00:07:09,137 --> 00:07:10,513
I SEE IT.

105
00:07:37,832 --> 00:07:39,376
SIR.

106
00:07:50,762 --> 00:07:54,308
JUDGING BY THE OXIDATION, THIS
HAPPENED ABOUT TWO WEEKS AGO.

107
00:07:54,308 --> 00:07:56,726
RIGHT ABOUT THE TIME
THE XINDI WERE HERE.

108
00:07:56,726 --> 00:07:58,728
IT'S DEFINITELY ONE OF THEIRS.

109
00:07:58,728 --> 00:08:01,022
I RECOGNIZE IT
FROM THE DATABASE.

110
00:08:02,523 --> 00:08:05,610
SEARCH THE AREA.
SEE WHAT ELSE YOU CAN FIND.

111
00:08:07,570 --> 00:08:10,031
SOME OF THEIR DATA BANKS
MAY STILL BE INTACT.

112
00:08:12,409 --> 00:08:13,701
CAPTAIN!

113
00:08:13,701 --> 00:08:15,329
A BODY.

114
00:08:19,416 --> 00:08:22,543
-[ BEEPING ]
-IT ISN'T XINDI.

115
00:08:22,543 --> 00:08:25,797
AT LEAST NOT ONE OF THE THREE
SPECIES WE'RE FAMILIAR WITH.

116
00:08:25,797 --> 00:08:27,841
MAYBE IT WAS
ONE OF THE OTHER TWO.

117
00:08:27,841 --> 00:08:30,051
WHAT ABOUT HIM?

118
00:08:34,681 --> 00:08:37,934
-[ BEEPING ]
-THE READINGS ARE THE SAME.

119
00:08:42,022 --> 00:08:45,566
THIS WHOLE AREA'S
BEEN SCORCHED.

120
00:08:45,566 --> 00:08:47,486
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

121
00:08:47,486 --> 00:08:48,695
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

122
00:08:48,695 --> 00:08:50,905
YEAH.

123
00:08:50,905 --> 00:08:53,658
I NEVER MUCH CARED
FOR THE TROPICS.

124
00:08:54,742 --> 00:08:56,661
KEEP LOOKING.

125
00:09:25,940 --> 00:09:27,650
LIEUTENANT?

126
00:09:30,445 --> 00:09:31,946
[ HISSES ]

127
00:09:34,741 --> 00:09:36,659
[ CHITTERS ]

128
00:09:38,036 --> 00:09:40,080
[ CHITTERING ]

129
00:09:59,516 --> 00:10:01,268
[ GRUNTING ]

130
00:10:11,903 --> 00:10:13,321
[ GROANING ]

131
00:10:15,782 --> 00:10:17,075
CAPTAIN!

132
00:10:23,081 --> 00:10:25,333
T'POL TO<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

133
00:10:25,333 --> 00:10:28,295
-GO AHEAD.
-Send a security team
to the surface.

134
00:10:28,295 --> 00:10:29,879
We're being altered
by some kind of --

135
00:10:29,879 --> 00:10:32,840
[ Speaking native language ]

136
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,342
SUBCOMMANDER?

137
00:10:43,101 --> 00:10:45,353
[ SPEAKING NATIVE LANGUAGE ]

138
00:10:46,605 --> 00:10:47,981
STAY BACK.

139
00:10:47,981 --> 00:10:49,732
[ SHOUTING IN NATIVE LANGUAGE ]

140
00:11:01,119 --> 00:11:02,412
[ CHOKING ]

141
00:11:02,412 --> 00:11:03,455
[ SNARLS ]

142
00:11:03,455 --> 00:11:04,831
[ GASPS ]

143
00:11:13,131 --> 00:11:14,466
[ SNARLS ]

144
00:11:16,801 --> 00:11:18,470
[ PANTING ]

145
00:11:38,865 --> 00:11:40,783
[ SPEAKING NATIVE LANGUAGE ]

146
00:12:07,894 --> 00:12:09,521
CAPTAIN --

147
00:12:16,027 --> 00:12:17,696
UNTIE ME.

148
00:12:18,863 --> 00:12:20,699
LET ME GO.

149
00:12:21,782 --> 00:12:23,368
[ CHITTERING ]

150
00:12:32,627 --> 00:12:33,961
[ SNARLING ]

151
00:12:46,933 --> 00:12:48,809
THANK YOU.

152
00:12:50,978 --> 00:12:53,064
[ SNIFFING ]

153
00:12:55,191 --> 00:12:57,860
[ CHITTERING ]

154
00:13:01,906 --> 00:13:03,908
WE HAVE TO GET BACK
TO<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

155
00:13:06,661 --> 00:13:08,622
<i>ENTERPRISE?</i>

156
00:13:15,462 --> 00:13:17,672
[ SPEAKING NATIVE LANGUAGE ]

157
00:13:25,138 --> 00:13:26,931
MAY I HAVE THAT?

158
00:13:26,931 --> 00:13:30,059
-[ HISSES ]
-THE DEVICE.
MAY I HAVE IT?

159
00:13:30,059 --> 00:13:32,270
[ SPEAKING NATIVE LANGUAGE ]

160
00:14:05,345 --> 00:14:07,263
[ BEEPING ]

161
00:14:10,099 --> 00:14:12,059
[ CHITTERING ]

162
00:14:14,979 --> 00:14:17,816
THIS MAY HELP US
UNDERSTAND EACH OTHER.

163
00:14:20,652 --> 00:14:23,446
YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE TO TALK.

164
00:14:26,825 --> 00:14:28,743
TALK.

165
00:14:31,746 --> 00:14:33,665
YOU NEED TO TALK.

166
00:14:45,677 --> 00:14:49,263
THAT'S A VULCAN BIO-SIGN.
I'M CERTAIN OF IT.

167
00:14:49,263 --> 00:14:50,348
BUT THESE AREN'T HUMAN.

168
00:14:50,348 --> 00:14:51,891
DEFINITELY NOT.

169
00:14:51,891 --> 00:14:55,019
THEN WHERE'S
THE REST OF OUR TEAM?

170
00:14:55,019 --> 00:14:57,814
THE ONLY REASON I DON'T
HAVE A SEARCH PARTY
DOWN THERE RIGHT NOW

171
00:14:57,814 --> 00:15:00,066
IS BECAUSE YOU NEEDED MORE TIME
TO ANALYZE THE DATA.

172
00:15:00,066 --> 00:15:02,360
NOW, UNLESS YOU CAN GIVE ME
A DAMN GOOD REASON
TO WAIT AROUND...

173
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:03,986
WHEN T'POL CALLED THE SHIP,

174
00:15:03,986 --> 00:15:05,655
SHE SAID SOMETHING
WAS HAPPENING TO THEM.

175
00:15:05,655 --> 00:15:07,490
SHE SAID THEY WERE
BEING ALTERED.

176
00:15:07,490 --> 00:15:09,784
IT'S POSSIBLE
SHE WAS SPEAKING LITERALLY.

177
00:15:09,784 --> 00:15:12,078
SOMETHING ON THE PLANET
MAY HAVE TRANSFORMED THEM,

178
00:15:12,078 --> 00:15:14,121
UH, PHYSIOLOGICALLY.

179
00:15:14,121 --> 00:15:16,916
YOU'RE SAYING THESE ALIEN
BIO-SIGNS COULD BE OUR PEOPLE?

180
00:15:16,916 --> 00:15:18,376
FROM WHAT WE'VE SEEN
OF THE EXPANSE,

181
00:15:18,376 --> 00:15:20,420
IT'S A POSSIBILITY
WE HAVE TO CONSIDER.

182
00:15:20,420 --> 00:15:22,839
THE LAWS OF BIOCHEMISTRY
ON THIS WORLD

183
00:15:22,839 --> 00:15:25,675
MAYBE JUST AS UNPREDICTABLE
AS THE LAWS OF PHYSICS.

184
00:15:25,675 --> 00:15:27,719
WHOEVER THEY ARE,
THEY'RE NOT STAYING PUT.

185
00:15:27,719 --> 00:15:30,638
THEY'RE HEADING DUE EAST
OF THE LANDING SITE.

186
00:15:31,848 --> 00:15:34,141
-PREP SHUTTLEPOD 2.
-AYE, SIR.

187
00:15:34,141 --> 00:15:36,227
I'D LIKE A LITTLE MORE TIME
TO STUDY THESE READINGS.

188
00:15:36,227 --> 00:15:38,438
WE'LL USE E.V. SUITS
WITH BIOHAZARD PROTOCOLS.

189
00:15:38,438 --> 00:15:41,065
HAVE THE DECON CHAMBER READY
WHEN WE GET BACK.

190
00:15:45,152 --> 00:15:48,155
<i>ENTERPRISE?</i>

191
00:15:48,155 --> 00:15:50,533
YES.
IT'S YOUR SHIP.

192
00:15:50,533 --> 00:15:52,368
YOU'RE THE CAPTAIN.

193
00:15:52,368 --> 00:15:55,204
WE DON'T HAVE TIME FOR THIS.

194
00:15:55,204 --> 00:15:58,291
WE HAVE TO FIND URQUAT.

195
00:15:58,291 --> 00:16:00,376
IT'S ALL THAT MATTERS NOW.

196
00:16:00,376 --> 00:16:02,169
URQUAT?

197
00:16:02,169 --> 00:16:04,338
WE HAVE TO KEEP LOOKING.

198
00:16:04,338 --> 00:16:06,633
IT'S SOMEWHERE CLOSE.

199
00:16:06,633 --> 00:16:09,218
WHY ARE YOU TALKING TO HER?

200
00:16:09,218 --> 00:16:11,262
SHE'S TRYING TO DELAY US.

201
00:16:11,262 --> 00:16:13,640
OUR PEOPLE ARE THERE.

202
00:16:18,895 --> 00:16:21,272
THEY CAN HELP US,

203
00:16:21,272 --> 00:16:26,235
TELL US WHAT HAPPENED,
WHY WE CAN'T REMEMBER.

204
00:16:27,528 --> 00:16:30,323
CAPTAIN, THAT DEVICE,

205
00:16:30,323 --> 00:16:32,199
I CAN USE IT TO CALL<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

206
00:16:32,199 --> 00:16:33,701
YOU HAVE A DOCTOR ON BOARD.

207
00:16:33,701 --> 00:16:35,578
HE CAN PROVE TO YOU
WHAT I'M SAYING IS TRUE.

208
00:16:35,578 --> 00:16:39,290
DON'T TRUST HER.
SHE'S NOT ONE OF US.

209
00:16:41,626 --> 00:16:45,588
WE DON'T KNOW WHAT SHE IS.

210
00:16:59,310 --> 00:17:00,394
URQUAT.

211
00:17:00,394 --> 00:17:02,396
[ GROWLS SOFTLY ]

212
00:17:02,396 --> 00:17:05,900
YOU SAID WE NEED
TO FIND URQUAT.

213
00:17:09,570 --> 00:17:12,031
WE SHOULD KEEP SEARCHING.

214
00:17:25,252 --> 00:17:27,046
IT CAN'T BE FAR.

215
00:17:38,224 --> 00:17:39,934
[ CHITTERING ]

216
00:18:07,086 --> 00:18:09,380
[ CHITTERING ]

217
00:18:09,380 --> 00:18:11,007
[ GROWLS ]

218
00:18:11,007 --> 00:18:12,383
[ GROWLS ]

219
00:18:15,011 --> 00:18:16,387
[ SNARLS ]

220
00:18:29,901 --> 00:18:31,027
[ GROWLS ]

221
00:18:48,002 --> 00:18:49,963
[ SNIFFS ]

222
00:19:03,476 --> 00:19:05,478
NO, THANK YOU.

223
00:19:10,149 --> 00:19:11,943
I'M NOT HUNGRY.

224
00:19:25,081 --> 00:19:26,499
[ CHITTERING ]

225
00:19:43,349 --> 00:19:47,145
THEY'RE ABOUT THREE KILOMETERS
EAST OF US.

226
00:19:47,145 --> 00:19:50,356
WE DON'T HAVE TOO MANY OPTIONS
FOR A LANDING SITE.

227
00:19:50,356 --> 00:19:53,275
HOPE YOU BOYS ARE UP
FOR A LITTLE WALK.

228
00:19:57,196 --> 00:19:58,990
[ WHIRRING ]

229
00:19:58,990 --> 00:20:01,241
IT'S A SHUTTLEPOD
FROM<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

230
00:20:01,241 --> 00:20:04,453
THEY WON'T HURT YOU.
LET ME TALK TO THEM.

231
00:20:16,049 --> 00:20:17,842
[ BEEPING ]

232
00:20:21,428 --> 00:20:23,556
KEEP YOUR WEAPONS ON STUN.

233
00:20:24,515 --> 00:20:26,642
CIRCLE AROUND.

234
00:20:42,700 --> 00:20:44,744
[ BEEPING ]

235
00:21:06,099 --> 00:21:07,516
[ CHITTERING ]

236
00:21:20,613 --> 00:21:22,531
CHANG.

237
00:21:22,531 --> 00:21:24,658
[ CHITTERING ]

238
00:21:31,082 --> 00:21:33,251
CAPTAIN!

239
00:21:33,251 --> 00:21:36,420
WAIT!
DON'T YOU RECOGNIZE HIM?

240
00:21:51,518 --> 00:21:53,437
TAKE LIEUTENANT REED
BACK TO SICK BAY.

241
00:21:53,437 --> 00:21:55,439
-WHAT ABOUT YOU?
-I'M STAYING WITH THEM.

242
00:21:55,439 --> 00:21:56,607
SUBCOMMANDER!

243
00:22:01,654 --> 00:22:03,156
[ SNARLING ]

244
00:22:05,283 --> 00:22:06,909
[ CHITTERING ]

245
00:22:15,960 --> 00:22:18,171
HE DIDN'T EVEN RECOGNIZE ME.

246
00:22:18,171 --> 00:22:20,131
DON'T BE OFFENDED.

247
00:22:20,131 --> 00:22:22,925
IN HIS CURRENT CONDITION, I
DOUBT HE'D RECOGNIZE ANY OF US.

248
00:22:22,925 --> 00:22:24,802
ANY IDEA WHAT CAUSED THIS?

249
00:22:24,802 --> 00:22:26,720
A MUTAGENIC VIRUS.

250
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:29,389
HIS BLOOD WAS SWARMING
WITH THEM.

251
00:22:34,352 --> 00:22:37,564
IT WAS APPARENTLY DESIGNED
TO REWRITE THE DNA OF ITS HOST

252
00:22:37,564 --> 00:22:40,901
TO TRANSFORM ANY HUMANOID
IT INFECTS INTO ANOTHER SPECIES.

253
00:22:40,901 --> 00:22:42,862
WHY DID IT HAVE
SO LITTLE EFFECT ON T'POL?

254
00:22:42,862 --> 00:22:44,322
VULCAN "K" CELLS.

255
00:22:44,322 --> 00:22:45,739
THEY SEEM TO NEUTRALIZE
THE PATHOGEN.

256
00:22:45,739 --> 00:22:47,700
I'VE BEEN SYNTHESIZING
AN ANTIVIRUS

257
00:22:47,700 --> 00:22:49,910
USING T'POL'S GENETIC PROFILE,
BUT I'M GOING TO NEED

258
00:22:49,910 --> 00:22:51,996
AN ACTIVE SAMPLE OF HER DNA
TO COMPLETE IT.

259
00:22:51,996 --> 00:22:54,372
WE NEED TO GET HER BACK
TO THE SHIP AS SOON AS POSSIBLE.

260
00:22:54,372 --> 00:22:55,749
I'M DOING MY BEST.

261
00:22:55,749 --> 00:22:57,417
-[ BEEPS ]
-Bridge to Commander Tucker.

262
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:01,547
GO AHEAD.

263
00:23:01,547 --> 00:23:03,299
Two ships just
dropped out of warp, sir.

264
00:23:03,299 --> 00:23:05,592
They're on an intercept course.

265
00:23:13,684 --> 00:23:15,644
[ BEEPING ]

266
00:23:15,644 --> 00:23:16,854
THEY'RE HAILING US.

267
00:23:16,854 --> 00:23:18,856
OPEN A CHANNEL.

268
00:23:18,856 --> 00:23:21,234
<i>YOUR SHIP IS</i>
<i>IN RESTRICTED SPACE.</i>

269
00:23:21,234 --> 00:23:24,486
SORRY.
IT WASN'T VERY WELL MARKED.

270
00:23:24,486 --> 00:23:26,864
<i>OUR SCANS INDICATE THAT ONE OF</i>
<i>THE PEOPLE ON YOUR SHIP</i>

271
00:23:26,864 --> 00:23:28,991
<i>HAS BEEN INFECTED</i>
<i>WITH A DANGEROUS VIRUS.</i>

272
00:23:28,991 --> 00:23:30,576
WE'RE AWARE OF THAT.

273
00:23:30,576 --> 00:23:32,703
IS THERE ANYTHING
YOU CAN TELL US ABOUT --

274
00:23:32,703 --> 00:23:34,830
<i>YOUR VESSEL</i>
<i>IS UNDER QUARANTINE.</i>

275
00:23:34,830 --> 00:23:36,290
<i>PREPARE TO BE BOARDED.</i>

276
00:23:43,047 --> 00:23:45,507
NO ONE'S COMING ABOARD
UNLESS I SAY SO.

277
00:23:45,507 --> 00:23:47,968
<i>THE INFECTED ORGANISM</i>
<i>MUST BE ERADICATED</i>

278
00:23:47,968 --> 00:23:50,179
<i>BEFORE THE VIRUS CAN SPREAD.</i>

279
00:23:50,179 --> 00:23:53,515
THAT INFECTED ORGANISM
IS A MEMBER OF MY CREW.

280
00:23:53,515 --> 00:23:55,601
<i>DOES HE STILL LOOK LIKE</i>
<i>ONE OF YOUR CREW?</i>

281
00:23:55,601 --> 00:23:59,521
<i>DOES HE RECOGNIZE YOU OR EVEN</i>
<i>SPEAK YOUR LANGUAGE ANYMORE?</i>

282
00:23:59,521 --> 00:24:01,815
<i>WE'VE BEEN STUDYING THE MUTAGEN</i>
<i>FOR 60 YEARS.</i>

283
00:24:01,815 --> 00:24:05,443
<i>THE ONLY COURSE OF ACTION</i>
<i>IS TO NEUTRALIZE THE OUTBREAK.</i>

284
00:24:05,443 --> 00:24:07,029
THERE ISN'T ANY OUTBREAK.

285
00:24:07,029 --> 00:24:09,323
LIEUTENANT REED IS
IN MEDICAL ISOLATION.

286
00:24:09,323 --> 00:24:11,325
<i>WE WON'T ALLOW YOUR VESSEL</i>
<i>TO LEAVE ORBIT</i>

287
00:24:11,325 --> 00:24:13,160
<i>WITH THE CONTAGION ABOARD.</i>

288
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:16,205
LOOK, WE'VE ONLY BEEN DEALING
WITH THIS VIRUS FOR ONE DAY.

289
00:24:16,205 --> 00:24:18,249
SO FORGIVE ME IF I DON'T
TAKE YOUR WORD FOR IT

290
00:24:18,249 --> 00:24:21,585
THAT THE ONLY OPTION IS TO
NEUTRALIZE OUR TACTICAL OFFICER.

291
00:24:21,585 --> 00:24:24,922
YOU WANT TO COME OVER TO DISCUSS
THE SITUATION, FINE.

292
00:24:24,922 --> 00:24:27,716
BUT IF YOU TRY TO FORCE YOUR WAY
ONTO THIS SHIP,

293
00:24:27,716 --> 00:24:30,761
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE ONE HELL
OF A FIGHT ON YOUR HANDS.

294
00:25:35,368 --> 00:25:36,785
[ FOOTSTEPS ]

295
00:25:39,913 --> 00:25:41,165
[ GASPS ]

296
00:25:44,835 --> 00:25:49,965
HOW LONG WAS I ASLEEP?

297
00:25:49,965 --> 00:25:52,843
ONLY FOR A FEW MINUTES.

298
00:25:52,843 --> 00:25:55,095
I SAW IT.

299
00:25:55,095 --> 00:26:00,393
IN MY DREAM, I WAS THERE.

300
00:26:00,393 --> 00:26:01,935
URQUAT?

301
00:26:01,935 --> 00:26:03,854
OUR CITY.

302
00:26:03,854 --> 00:26:06,773
THERE ARE NO CITIES
ON THIS PLANET.

303
00:26:06,773 --> 00:26:08,734
YOU'RE WRONG.

304
00:26:09,943 --> 00:26:12,488
IT'S BELOW THE SURFACE.

305
00:26:12,488 --> 00:26:13,906
TELL ME.

306
00:26:17,368 --> 00:26:19,453
WHAT WAS IT LIKE?

307
00:26:19,453 --> 00:26:26,544
IT WAS FILLED
WITH THOUSANDS OF LOQUE'EQUE.

308
00:26:26,544 --> 00:26:27,711
WAITING.

309
00:26:29,838 --> 00:26:31,798
FOR US.

310
00:26:33,300 --> 00:26:36,887
YOUR HOME
IS A PLANET CALLED EARTH.

311
00:26:36,887 --> 00:26:40,224
THE PEOPLE THERE
ARE WAITING FOR YOU.

312
00:26:40,224 --> 00:26:43,519
YOU'RE ON A MISSION
TO SAVE THEM.

313
00:26:44,937 --> 00:26:47,356
URQUAT'S MY HOME.

314
00:26:47,356 --> 00:26:49,900
WHEN WE GET THERE,
YOU'LL UNDERSTAND.

315
00:26:49,900 --> 00:26:51,693
WAIT AND SEE.

316
00:26:53,279 --> 00:26:55,739
WE'VE RESTED LONG ENOUGH.

317
00:26:57,741 --> 00:26:58,951
THE DECON CHAMBER IS SEALED.

318
00:26:58,951 --> 00:27:00,953
I ASSURE YOU,
THERE'S NO DANGER.

319
00:27:00,953 --> 00:27:02,455
YOU WOULDN'T BE SO CONFIDENT

320
00:27:02,455 --> 00:27:05,124
IF YOU KNEW HOW EASILY
THIS VIRUS CAN SPREAD.

321
00:27:05,124 --> 00:27:07,918
IT INFECTED TENS OF MILLIONS
OF PEOPLE ON MY WORLD.

322
00:27:07,918 --> 00:27:10,837
THEY ALL HAD TO BE DESTROYED.

323
00:27:10,837 --> 00:27:12,172
DESTROYED?

324
00:27:12,172 --> 00:27:13,673
THE VIRUS WOULD HAVE TRANSFORMED

325
00:27:13,673 --> 00:27:15,926
OUR ENTIRE POPULATION
WITHIN WEEKS.

326
00:27:17,010 --> 00:27:19,221
WHERE DID IT COME FROM?

327
00:27:19,221 --> 00:27:21,890
IT WAS ENGINEERED BY
THE INHABITANTS OF THIS PLANET,

328
00:27:21,890 --> 00:27:24,893
A RACE CALLED THE LOQUE'EQUE.

329
00:27:24,893 --> 00:27:27,438
SOMETHING DECIMATED
THEIR SPECIES CENTURIES AGO,

330
00:27:27,438 --> 00:27:29,898
AND THEY LOST THE ABILITY
TO REPRODUCE.

331
00:27:29,898 --> 00:27:31,317
SO THEY CREATED THIS VIRUS

332
00:27:31,317 --> 00:27:33,444
TO TRANSFORM OTHER SPECIES
INTO THEIR OWN.

333
00:27:33,444 --> 00:27:36,530
IT WAS THE ONLY WAY TO SAVE
THEMSELVES FROM EXTINCTION.

334
00:27:36,530 --> 00:27:38,282
INGENIOUS.

335
00:27:38,282 --> 00:27:40,367
BUT WHY DIDN'T THEY PROGRAM
THE VIRUS TO STOP REPLICATING

336
00:27:40,367 --> 00:27:42,328
ONCE THEIR POPULATION
WAS REPLENISHED?

337
00:27:42,328 --> 00:27:45,205
WE'VE BEEN TRYING TO ANSWER
THAT QUESTION FOR A LONG TIME.

338
00:27:45,205 --> 00:27:48,834
WHY'S HE SO EAGER TO GET BACK
TO A PLACE CALLED URQUAT?

339
00:27:48,834 --> 00:27:51,837
THE MUTAGEN ENCODES THE VICTIMS
WITH AN OVERPOWERING INSTINCT

340
00:27:51,837 --> 00:27:54,714
TO RETURN
TO THEIR HOME CITY, URQUAT.

341
00:27:54,714 --> 00:27:57,301
THAT'S WHY WE CAN'T ALLOW
EVEN A SINGLE INFECTED ORGANISM

342
00:27:57,301 --> 00:27:59,094
TO LEAVE THIS PLANET.

343
00:27:59,094 --> 00:28:00,846
THEY COULD SPREAD THE CONTAGION
TO OTHER SYSTEMS,

344
00:28:00,846 --> 00:28:04,183
AND ANYONE WHO BECAME INFECTED
WOULD BE DRAWN BACK HERE.

345
00:28:04,183 --> 00:28:06,810
WE CAN'T RISK ANOTHER EPIDEMIC.

346
00:28:06,810 --> 00:28:08,562
[ COMMUNICATOR BEEPS ]

347
00:28:10,397 --> 00:28:12,274
YES?

348
00:28:12,274 --> 00:28:14,985
We've detected three more
infected organisms
on the surface.

349
00:28:14,985 --> 00:28:17,571
PREPARE A CONTAINMENT TEAM.

350
00:28:17,571 --> 00:28:19,072
MORE OF YOUR CREWMEN?

351
00:28:19,072 --> 00:28:21,283
ONE OF THEM HAS AN IMMUNITY
TO THE VIRUS.

352
00:28:21,283 --> 00:28:23,243
IF I COULD HAVE ACCESS
TO SOME OF YOUR RESEARCH,

353
00:28:23,243 --> 00:28:24,786
PERHAPS WE COULD WORK TOGETHER.

354
00:28:24,786 --> 00:28:27,540
WE'LL FIND THESE PEOPLE
AND EXAMINE THEM.

355
00:28:27,540 --> 00:28:30,083
IF THERE'S ANYTHING TO REPORT,
WE'LL LET YOU KNOW.

356
00:28:30,083 --> 00:28:32,919
I'D PREFER TO HAVE
DR. PHLOX EXAMINE THEM.

357
00:28:32,919 --> 00:28:35,214
WHAT YOU PREFER DOESN'T MATTER.

358
00:28:35,214 --> 00:28:38,133
I'M UNDER ORDERS
TO CONTAIN THIS OUTBREAK.

359
00:28:38,133 --> 00:28:40,219
IF YOU ATTEMPT TO INTERFERE,

360
00:28:40,219 --> 00:28:43,514
I'M AUTHORIZED TO USE
ANY FORCE NECESSARY.

361
00:28:48,060 --> 00:28:50,646
TAKE ME BACK TO THE AIRLOCK.

362
00:28:59,321 --> 00:29:01,156
IF I DON'T COMPLETE
THE ANTIVIRUS

363
00:29:01,156 --> 00:29:03,325
WITHIN THE NEXT TWO HOURS,
IT'LL BE TOO LATE.

364
00:29:03,325 --> 00:29:05,202
THERE WON'T BE ENOUGH
OF THEIR ORIGINAL GENOME LEFT

365
00:29:05,202 --> 00:29:06,870
TO RESEQUENCE.

366
00:29:06,870 --> 00:29:09,831
WE CAN'T LAUNCH A SHUTTLEPOD.
THEY'D DETECT IT.

367
00:29:09,831 --> 00:29:12,876
[ SIGHS ]
DO YOU THINK T'POL'S CONTAGIOUS?

368
00:29:12,876 --> 00:29:14,336
MOST LIKELY.

369
00:29:14,336 --> 00:29:16,963
THAT RULES OUT THE TRANSPORTER.

370
00:29:16,963 --> 00:29:19,174
SHE'D INFECT THE ENTIRE CREW.

371
00:29:19,174 --> 00:29:20,551
WHATEVER YOU DO, COMMANDER,
DO IT QUICKLY.

372
00:29:20,551 --> 00:29:22,302
I NEED THAT DNA SAMPLE.

373
00:29:26,139 --> 00:29:28,100
BE RIGHT BACK.

374
00:29:51,749 --> 00:29:53,751
-[ BEEPS ]
-Bridge to Commander Tucker.

375
00:29:53,751 --> 00:29:55,461
GO AHEAD.

376
00:29:55,461 --> 00:29:57,129
One of those ships
just launched a shuttle, sir.

377
00:29:57,129 --> 00:29:58,880
It's heading toward the surface.

378
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:00,090
KEEP AN EYE ON 'EM.

379
00:30:00,090 --> 00:30:02,926
[ PANTING ]

380
00:30:02,926 --> 00:30:05,845
IT ISN'T FAR NOW.

381
00:30:13,395 --> 00:30:16,856
THE PASSAGE WAS HERE
IN MY DREAM.

382
00:30:18,150 --> 00:30:19,443
HELP ME.

383
00:31:22,088 --> 00:31:24,966
YOU SAID THEY'D BE
WAITING FOR US.

384
00:31:24,966 --> 00:31:28,928
I...SAW IT...

385
00:31:28,928 --> 00:31:31,348
SO C-CLEARLY.

386
00:31:31,348 --> 00:31:37,354
THERE WAS...A FOUNTAIN THERE.

387
00:31:38,271 --> 00:31:42,192
AND GARDENS.

388
00:31:42,192 --> 00:31:44,611
UP THERE.

389
00:31:44,611 --> 00:31:46,279
FLOATING.

390
00:31:48,532 --> 00:31:52,578
AND THERE WERE...PEOPLE.

391
00:31:54,120 --> 00:31:58,083
THOUSANDS OF PEOPLE!

392
00:31:58,083 --> 00:31:59,793
COME BACK TO<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

393
00:31:59,793 --> 00:32:02,546
WE'LL HELP YOU FIND OUT
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOUR CITY.

394
00:32:02,546 --> 00:32:04,214
NO! NO!

395
00:32:04,214 --> 00:32:07,593
WE'RE NOT LEAVING.
THIS IS OUR HOME.

396
00:32:07,593 --> 00:32:10,429
HOME. HOME.

397
00:32:16,810 --> 00:32:19,688
LOOK AROUND.

398
00:32:19,688 --> 00:32:22,065
THESE RUINS ARE ANCIENT.

399
00:32:22,065 --> 00:32:25,861
NO ONE HAS LIVED HERE
FOR A VERY LONG TIME.

400
00:32:28,614 --> 00:32:30,240
WHAT ABOUT THIS?

401
00:32:30,240 --> 00:32:34,244
THIS BODY ISN'T ANCIENT.

402
00:32:38,331 --> 00:32:41,710
SOMEONE KILLED THEM.

403
00:32:41,710 --> 00:32:43,044
WHY?

404
00:32:45,046 --> 00:32:48,133
WHO WOULD DO THIS?

405
00:32:58,727 --> 00:33:01,271
YOUR PEOPLE?

406
00:33:02,564 --> 00:33:04,942
-NO.
-THEN WHO?

407
00:33:04,942 --> 00:33:06,735
I DON'T KNOW.

408
00:33:06,735 --> 00:33:09,321
BUT IF WE GO TO<i> ENTERPRISE,</i>
WE CAN TRY TO FIND OUT.

409
00:33:09,321 --> 00:33:11,949
I DON'T BELONG ON<i> ENTERPRISE!</i>

410
00:33:11,949 --> 00:33:14,534
I BELONG HERE.

411
00:33:14,534 --> 00:33:16,495
SOMEONE'S COMING.

412
00:33:16,495 --> 00:33:20,081
MORE OF YOUR HUMANS?

413
00:33:20,081 --> 00:33:22,918
I DON'T THINK SO.

414
00:33:27,881 --> 00:33:29,967
WE'RE NOT SAFE HERE.

415
00:33:29,967 --> 00:33:33,011
COME.
WE MUST GO.

416
00:33:33,011 --> 00:33:34,680
COME. WE MUST GO.

417
00:33:47,484 --> 00:33:49,277
WE FOUND THEM.

418
00:33:49,277 --> 00:33:52,155
Take the Vulcan woman.
Then destroy the others.

419
00:33:52,155 --> 00:33:53,949
UNDERSTOOD.

420
00:33:56,075 --> 00:33:58,119
WHO ARE THEY?

421
00:33:58,119 --> 00:33:59,913
I DON'T KNOW.

422
00:34:28,483 --> 00:34:32,445
YOU DESTROYED MY CITY!
KILLED MY PEOPLE!

423
00:34:37,910 --> 00:34:38,952
[ GAS HISSING ]

424
00:34:42,121 --> 00:34:44,249
CAPTAIN!

425
00:34:44,249 --> 00:34:46,209
WE HAVE TO GET
TO THE SURFACE.

426
00:35:11,985 --> 00:35:13,612
THIS WAY.

427
00:35:17,115 --> 00:35:18,951
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

428
00:35:23,288 --> 00:35:25,040
NO. NO.

429
00:35:26,499 --> 00:35:28,043
NO.

430
00:35:28,043 --> 00:35:31,421
NO!
[ SCREAMING ]

431
00:35:46,645 --> 00:35:51,108
LOWER YOUR WEAPON AND MOVE AWAY.
YOU WON'T BE HARMED.

432
00:35:51,108 --> 00:35:53,192
I SAID MOVE AWAY!

433
00:35:53,192 --> 00:35:54,569
AAH!

434
00:36:00,325 --> 00:36:01,743
[ SNARLS ]

435
00:36:15,214 --> 00:36:17,134
YOU ALL RIGHT?

436
00:36:17,134 --> 00:36:20,470
YOU SAID YOU'D NEVER
USE THE TRANSPORTER AGAIN.

437
00:36:20,470 --> 00:36:22,305
BELIEVE ME,
I WISH I'D HAD A CHOICE.

438
00:36:22,305 --> 00:36:23,807
THERE ARE MORE OF THEM IN ORBIT.

439
00:36:23,807 --> 00:36:25,266
WE'D BETTER GET BACK
TO THE SHUTTLEPOD

440
00:36:25,266 --> 00:36:27,894
BEFORE THEY REALIZE
ANYTHING'S WRONG.

441
00:36:29,896 --> 00:36:32,273
CAPTAIN.

442
00:36:32,273 --> 00:36:34,233
YOU CAN'T STAY HERE.

443
00:36:34,233 --> 00:36:37,403
YOU'LL BE SAFE ON<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

444
00:36:54,046 --> 00:36:55,964
[ BEEPING ]

445
00:36:55,964 --> 00:36:57,382
IT'S COMMANDER TUCKER.

446
00:36:57,382 --> 00:36:59,926
PUT HIM THROUGH.

447
00:36:59,926 --> 00:37:01,720
GO AHEAD, SIR.

448
00:37:01,720 --> 00:37:04,764
We're docking, Travis.
Tell Phlox to stand by in decon.

449
00:37:04,764 --> 00:37:07,142
Go to warp 4
as soon as we're in.

450
00:37:07,142 --> 00:37:08,810
UNDERSTOOD.

451
00:37:27,662 --> 00:37:29,206
REPORT.

452
00:37:29,206 --> 00:37:32,209
THEY'RE IN PURSUIT.
2,000 KILOMETERS AND CLOSING.

453
00:37:32,209 --> 00:37:34,002
TRY TO STAY AHEAD OF 'EM.

454
00:37:34,002 --> 00:37:35,503
STAND BY WEAPONS.

455
00:37:42,010 --> 00:37:43,595
THEY'RE HAILING US.

456
00:37:43,595 --> 00:37:45,805
DON'T RESPOND.
HOLD YOUR COURSE.

457
00:37:48,183 --> 00:37:49,684
900 KILOMETERS.

458
00:37:49,684 --> 00:37:51,186
THEY'RE CHARGING WEAPONS!

459
00:37:51,186 --> 00:37:53,105
700.

460
00:37:53,105 --> 00:37:54,272
[ EXPLOSION ]

461
00:37:54,272 --> 00:37:55,857
FULL POWER TO AFT HULL PLATING!

462
00:38:06,367 --> 00:38:08,453
HULL PLATING'S DOWN TO 40%.

463
00:38:08,453 --> 00:38:11,206
-[ BEEPING ]
-WE'RE BEING HAILED AGAIN.

464
00:38:14,417 --> 00:38:15,710
<i>DROP OUT OF WARP.</i>

465
00:38:15,710 --> 00:38:19,422
LOOK, WE BOTH WANT
THE SAME THING --

466
00:38:19,422 --> 00:38:20,882
A CURE FOR THIS VIRUS, RIGHT?

467
00:38:20,882 --> 00:38:22,550
OUR DOCTOR THINKS
HE'S FOUND ONE,

468
00:38:22,550 --> 00:38:24,094
BUT HE NEEDS
A LITTLE MORE TIME.

469
00:38:24,094 --> 00:38:26,054
<i>I WON'T WARN YOU AGAIN,</i>
<i>COMMANDER.</i>

470
00:38:26,054 --> 00:38:27,597
<i>WE'RE GOING TO</i>
<i>CONTAIN THIS OUTBREAK</i>

471
00:38:27,597 --> 00:38:29,849
<i>WHETHER YOU COOPERATE OR NOT.</i>

472
00:38:33,603 --> 00:38:35,897
WHY ARE YOU FIRING
AT MY SHIP?

473
00:38:35,897 --> 00:38:38,066
<i>THERE ARE THREE INFECTED PEOPLE</i>
<i>ON BOARD.</i>

474
00:38:38,066 --> 00:38:40,693
<i>WE WON'T ALLOW YOU</i>
<i>TO LEAVE THIS SYSTEM.</i>

475
00:38:40,693 --> 00:38:43,029
THIS IS CAPTAIN ARCHER
AND ENSIGN SATO.

476
00:38:43,029 --> 00:38:45,991
THEY'RE THE PEOPLE YOU NEARLY
INCINERATED ON THAT PLANET.

477
00:38:45,991 --> 00:38:48,409
AS YOU CAN SEE,
THEY'RE RESPONDING QUITE WELL

478
00:38:48,409 --> 00:38:50,162
TO THE ANTIVIRUS I SYNTHESIZED.

479
00:38:50,162 --> 00:38:52,330
<i>THAT'S NOT POSSIBLE.</i>

480
00:38:52,330 --> 00:38:56,960
RUN SCANS.
SEE FOR YOURSELF.

481
00:38:56,960 --> 00:39:00,046
LIKE I SAID, HE JUST NEEDED
A LITTLE MORE TIME.

482
00:39:01,923 --> 00:39:04,467
I'M SURE WE'D BE HAPPY TO SHARE
THE ANTIVIRUS WITH YOU.

483
00:39:04,467 --> 00:39:07,637
BUT THAT'LL BE IMPOSSIBLE
IF YOU DESTROY OUR SHIP.

484
00:39:10,307 --> 00:39:12,475
CAPTAIN'S STARLOG,
SUPPLEMENTAL.

485
00:39:12,475 --> 00:39:14,144
WE'VE GIVEN PHLOX'S SERUM

486
00:39:14,144 --> 00:39:15,937
TO THE CAPTAIN
OF THE CONTAINMENT VESSEL.

487
00:39:15,937 --> 00:39:18,315
WITH ANY LUCK,
THEY'LL BE ABLE TO USE IT

488
00:39:18,315 --> 00:39:19,983
TO PREVENT FUTURE OUTBREAKS.

489
00:39:19,983 --> 00:39:22,027
AS FOR MALCOLM, HOSHI, AND ME,

490
00:39:22,027 --> 00:39:25,989
IT MAY BE A FEW DAYS BEFORE
WE FEEL FULLY HUMAN AGAIN.

491
00:39:25,989 --> 00:39:27,324
[ CLICKS ]

492
00:39:27,324 --> 00:39:29,201
THIS SHOULD HELP
WITH THE HEADACHES.

493
00:39:29,201 --> 00:39:31,119
HAVE YOU GOT ANYTHING
FOR MY STOMACH?

494
00:39:31,119 --> 00:39:33,788
CHEF'S FOOD
ISN'T SITTING TOO WELL.

495
00:39:33,788 --> 00:39:36,041
TILL YOUR DIGESTIVE TRACT
IS FULLY RESTORED,

496
00:39:36,041 --> 00:39:38,751
YOU MAY WANT TO AVOID
THE MESS HALL.

497
00:39:38,751 --> 00:39:40,753
WHAT DO YOU SUGGEST I EAT?

498
00:39:40,753 --> 00:39:42,839
YOU'RE WELCOME
TO SOME OF THE MOTH LARVAE

499
00:39:42,839 --> 00:39:45,258
I FEED MY PYRITHIAN BAT.

500
00:39:47,426 --> 00:39:48,594
[ GRUNTS ]

501
00:39:49,762 --> 00:39:52,431
HOW ARE YOU FEELING,
LIEUTENANT?

502
00:39:52,431 --> 00:39:56,228
NOT BAD, SIR.
HOW ABOUT YOURSELF?

503
00:39:57,354 --> 00:39:59,022
GETTING THERE.

504
00:39:59,022 --> 00:40:01,816
HOSHI AND T'POL
ARE GONNA TAKE THE DAY OFF.

505
00:40:01,816 --> 00:40:04,277
YOU MIGHT WANT TO DO THE SAME.

506
00:40:04,277 --> 00:40:08,907
THANK YOU, CAPTAIN.
I COULD USE A LITTLE REST.

507
00:40:13,828 --> 00:40:15,580
YOU WANTED TO SEE ME?

508
00:40:17,123 --> 00:40:19,417
THIS IS THE LAST
OF THE MUTAGENIC VIRUS.

509
00:40:19,417 --> 00:40:21,753
I ASSUME YOU WANT ME
TO DESTROY IT.

510
00:40:22,921 --> 00:40:24,089
NO.

511
00:40:24,089 --> 00:40:25,965
CAPTAIN,
YOU EXPERIENCED FIRSTHAND

512
00:40:25,965 --> 00:40:27,550
WHAT THIS PATHOGEN CAN DO.

513
00:40:27,550 --> 00:40:31,388
THOSE CONTAINMENT PATROLS
AREN'T GOING TO STOP

514
00:40:31,388 --> 00:40:33,265
UNTIL THEY'VE WIPED OUT
EVERY TRACE OF IT.

515
00:40:33,265 --> 00:40:36,017
NOW THAT THEY HAVE
YOUR ANTIVIRUS,

516
00:40:36,017 --> 00:40:38,311
THEY'LL MOST LIKELY FIGURE OUT
A WAY TO SUCCEED.

517
00:40:38,311 --> 00:40:41,147
CONSIDERING THE ALTERNATIVES,
THAT WOULD BE BEST.

518
00:40:49,488 --> 00:40:54,452
THIS WAS CREATED
AS A FINAL EFFORT

519
00:40:54,452 --> 00:40:58,497
TO PRESERVE A CIVILIZATION,
A-A PEOPLE.

520
00:40:59,707 --> 00:41:02,168
THAT SPECIES WE BECAME...

521
00:41:03,836 --> 00:41:06,505
...THEY CEASE TO EXIST
THE MOMENT THIS VIRUS IS GONE.

522
00:41:06,505 --> 00:41:07,840
CAPTAIN...

523
00:41:10,093 --> 00:41:13,846
WE CAME OUT HERE TO STOP THE
XINDI FROM DESTROYING HUMANITY.

524
00:41:13,846 --> 00:41:16,891
I'LL BE DAMNED
IF I'M GONNA HAVE A HAND

525
00:41:16,891 --> 00:41:20,979
IN DESTROYING ANOTHER RACE
IN THE PROCESS.

526
00:41:24,190 --> 00:41:26,234
PUT IT ON ICE, DOC.

527
00:41:26,234 --> 00:41:28,527
IN STASIS, WHATEVER.

528
00:41:28,527 --> 00:41:30,071
UNDERSTOOD?
